      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Compliance Scorecard by STIG + Benchmark Currency\n**Question:** per-STIG, how compliant are we and **are we on the latest benchmark revision?** The table joins the collection's in-use STIGs to the STIG **library** \u2014 compare *Rev in use* vs *Latest rev*. `Pinned = true` means the collection is frozen on an old revision (on purpose, or by neglect)."
      },
      "transparent": true,
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Collection at a glance",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Collection CORA (risk)",
      "description": "Weighted risk score, lower is better.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "stigmanager-prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "stigmanager-prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "stigman_collection_cora_percent{collection_name=~\"${collection:text}\"}",
          "editorMode": "code",
          "legendFormat": "__auto",
          "range": true,
          "instant": false
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "decimals": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "#0ca30c",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "#fab219",
                "value": 20
              },
              {
                "color": "#d03b3b",
                "value": 40
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Coverage %",
      "description": "Assessed / required.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
